{
  "value": "FIRESIDE",
  "label": "Fireside",
  "description": "Design-chat / fireside transcripts (DESIGN.md §5.4). v3 (CASE-481): identity is the KB-minted `fireside_number` (per-type sequence, synonym FIRESIDE-<n>) — title/topic become mutable. topic gets FTS weight A for topic-page aggregation. chat_date separates when-the-chat-happened from when-it-was-persisted.",
